{"type":"message","id":"93f6af15","parentId":"d5ad1459","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:58:38.245Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_whb1vkwoehkg_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Hot reload for config, cold sweat for deploys.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3199,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Hot reload for config, cold sweat for deploys.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\hou-zu\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773921518241}}
{"type":"message","id":"90713536","parentId":"93f6af15","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:58:40.136Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我看看 cron add 命令的帮助。","thinkingSignature":"5916ff43726fc1d8f3dd449c1f701b58cd66b8095f0477bfdd6ebf42a4bc8dc3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f4fjfi65648w_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --help"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":7804,"output":38,"cacheRead":31797,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39639,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773921518246}}
{"type":"message","id":"249923df","parentId":"90713536","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:58:42.937Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f4fjfi65648w_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Your config is valid, your assumptions are not.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2794,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Your config is valid, your assumptions are not.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\hou-zu\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773921522934}}
{"type":"message","id":"fdb0d072","parentId":"249923df","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:59:23.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我可以使用 `openclaw cron add` 命令创建定时任务。我需要：- `--cron \"0 * * * *\"` - 每小时整点执行\n- `--message` - 执行的消息/命令- `--agent` - 使用的 Agent\n- `--announce` - 交付到群里\n- `--to` - 群 ID\n\n对于自动上传 GitHub，我可以创建一个 agent 任务，让它执行 git 命令。但是，使用 agentTurn 来执行 git 命令可能比较复杂。\n\n让我看看是否可以使用 `--system-event` 或其他方式来执行 shell 命令。\n\n实际上，根据之前的 jobs.json，这些任务都是 agentTurn 类型的。让我创建一个 agent 任务来执行 git 上传。\n\n但是使用 cron add 创建的任务是发送到 Agent 的，不是直接执行 shell 命令。我需要考虑另一种方式。\n\n让我看看 jobs.json 中的配置方式是否支持 shell 类型。或者我可以创建一个 Agent 任务，让 Agent 执行 git 上传。\n\n最简单的方式是：创建一个 agentTurn 任务，让 Agent（后助）执行 git 上传命令。\n\n让我先准备审批申请。根据 skill 要求，我需要提交测试记录，然后联系管管审批。\n\n## 测试记录\n- 测试时间: 2026-03-19 19:57\n- 测试次数: 1\n\n\n- 结果: ✅成功\n- 错误信息: 无\n\n手动执行 `git add -A; git commit -m \"chore: 自动上传\"; git push` 成功。现在我需要为这个 cron 任务准备审批申请，指定执行频率为每小时整点。\n\n任务需要设置超时为 120 秒，交付模式采用 announce 并发布到飞书群。我会用 Agent 来执行 git 命令，在提交前需要先确认审批的格式。","thinkingSignature":"185702f41ee6b02a3122b096609dd94fbf0cee9529064ac41d5347b8ab23bd84"},{"type":"text","text":"让我创建测试记录并准备审批申请：\n\n## 测试记录\n- **测试时间**: 2026-03-19 19:57\n- **测试次数**: 1\n- **结果**: ✅成功\n- **错误信息**: 无\n- **调整内容**: 无\n\n手动执行命令测试成功：\n```bash\ngit add -A && git commit -m \"chore: 测试自动上传\" && git push\n```\n\n---\n\n## 任务创建申请\n- **任务**: 每小时自动上传 GitHub\n- **类型**: cron\n- **频率**: `0 * * * *` (每小时整点)\n- **超时**: 120秒\n- **投递**: announce (飞书群)\n- **测试**: ✅成功\n\n**任务配置**:\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"每小时自动上传 GitHub\",\n  \"schedule\": \"0 * * * *\",\n  \"agentId\": \"hou-zu\",\n  \"message\": \"自动上传所有更改到 GitHub。执行: cd C:\\\\Users\\\\16343\\\\.openclaw && git add -A && git commit -m \\\"chore: 自动同步\\\" && git push\",\n  \"timeoutSeconds\": 120,\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n@管管 请审批这个定时任务。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-